SELECT d.Data + ' (' + (SELECT d2.Data FROM Subjects s2 INNER JOIN DataPages dpages2 ON dpages2.SubjectID=s2.SubjectID INNER JOIN Forms fr2 ON dpages2.FormID=fr2.FormID INNER JOIN Records r2 ON r2.DataPageID=dpages2.DataPageID INNER JOIN DataPoints d2 ON d2.RecordID=r2.RecordID INNER JOIN Fields fi2 ON d2.FieldID=fi2.FieldID WHERE s2.SubjectID='{subjectid}' AND fr2.OID='AE' AND fi2.OID='AESTDTC' AND r2.RecordID = r.RecordID) + ')'
,d.Data + ' (' + (SELECT d2.Data FROM Subjects s2 INNER JOIN DataPages dpages2 ON dpages2.SubjectID=s2.SubjectID INNER JOIN Forms fr2 ON dpages2.FormID=fr2.FormID INNER JOIN Records r2 ON r2.DataPageID=dpages2.DataPageID INNER JOIN DataPoints d2 ON d2.RecordID=r2.RecordID INNER JOIN Fields fi2 ON d2.FieldID=fi2.FieldID WHERE s2.SubjectID='{subjectid}' AND fr2.OID='AE' AND fi2.OID='AESTDTC' AND r2.RecordID = r.RecordID) + ')'
FROM Subjects s INNER JOIN DataPages dpages ON dpages.SubjectID=s.SubjectID INNER JOIN Forms fr ON dpages.FormID=fr.FormID INNER JOIN Records r ON r.DataPageID=dpages.DataPageID INNER JOIN DataPoints d ON d.RecordID=r.RecordID INNER JOIN Fields fi ON d.FieldID=fi.FieldID
WHERE s.SubjectID= '{subjectid}' AND fr.OID='AE' AND fi.OID='AETERM' AND d.dataactive = 1 AND r.recordactive = 1 AND dpages.datapageactive = 1 AND r.RecordPosition <> 0
